chnology-and-education">Technology and education</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref14925"><a class="w-100 link-gray-900" href="/technology/history-of-technology/Technology-and-education#ref14925">The quality of life</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></li></ul>
                    
                    
                

                

                
